{"title":"炊具改革见奇功","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊具改革见奇功"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑水切菜做饭忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年来是这样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公共食堂诞生后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊具革新大变样："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器一动菜切好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清水引到锅灶旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边做饭来边学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭熟菜香人欢畅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊具改革好处大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做饭都用机械化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节省人力搞生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增产更比去年多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动力磨，好处多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人能干九人活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前推磨人十个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今一人还嫌多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小马达凶又凶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带动五磨跑如风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一日能磨千斤面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造发明见奇功。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}